Introduction

Park Sujin, more popularly known as Swan, is a South Korean singer signed with RBW. She is the Main Vocalist and Maknae of the girl group PURPLE KISS.

She debuted with PURPLE KISS on March 15, 2021, with the mini album “INTO VIOLET”, with the title track “Ponzona”.

Swan also appeared on various television programs. In 2022, she joined Mnet’s music survival show “Artistock Game”, and in 2023, Kakao’s one-of-a-kind virtual survival program “GIRL'S RE:VERSE”.

On July 2, 2023, Swan made her solo debut with the digital single “Twenty".
